data.description: Welcome to a residence where elegance meets comfort, a haven that seamlessly blends spacious living with modern convenience. Boasting an expansive 2,800 square feet, this residence unfolds across two levels, providing ample space for both privacy and shared moments. With four generously sized bedrooms and two and a half baths. Step into the heart of the home, where a harmonious blend of style and functionality awaits.     The gourmet kitchen, with stainless steel appliances and hard-surface countertops, is a culinary enthusiast's dream, featuring an island that beckons for gatherings. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the kitchen to the inviting living space, adorned with large windows that flood the area with natural light. In addition to the well-appointed interiors, this property is complemented by a two-car garage, providing convenience and shelter for your vehicles. As you step outside, a delightful surprise awaits-an exquisite pagoda that stays with the house.     This charming outdoor space invites you to savor the beauty of the surrounding landscape Situated in a community known for its friendly atmosphere and proximity to amenities, this residence not only offers a comfortable dwelling but a lifestyle that harmonizes with the desires of modern living. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home-a place where cherished memories are waiting to be created. Welcome to a residence that transcends the ordinary, where every detail has been curated to enhance your living experience.
